Customer Notices
Evening hearings for the purpose of receiving public comment on Pepco’s application for adjustments to its Maryland retail rates for the distribution of electric energy are scheduled for 6:30 p.m. Aug. 28 (Prince George’s County Community College, Largo Student Center, Room 227 – Community Room B, 301 Largo Road, Largo, Maryland, Maryland 20774) and 6:30 p.m. Aug. 30 (Montgomery County Council Office Building, Third Floor Hearing Room, 100 Maryland Avenue, Rockville, Maryland, 20850). Written comments may also be filed by Sept. 15.







