Investor Relations









Corporate ProfilePepco Holdings, Inc. (PHI) (NYSE: POM) is one of the largest energy
delivery companies in the Mid-Atlantic region, serving about 2
million customers in Delaware, the District of Columbia, Maryland and New
Jersey. 
PHI subsidiaries Pepco, Delmarva
Power and Atlantic City Electric provide regulated electricity serviceDelmarva Power also provides natural
gas service 
PHI also provides energy efficiency and
renewable energy services through Pepco Energy Services, Inc.
		



























