ShareOverviewSummaryPepco Energy Services, Inc. has worked on seventy-two contracts worth $114 million USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2012), the organization received a total of $3.46 million USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Defense, Department of Commerce, and General Services Administration.

