Higher Than AverageThe principal NAICS category of Pepco Energy Services, Inc. is Other Electric Power Generation (221119) as measured by the total amount obligated in contract awards to the vendor since FY2007.In its latest full year of contract work (FY2012), Pepco Energy Services, Inc. was obligated a total of $3.46M, an amount that was far higher than the average vendor from District of Columbia specializing in Other Electric Power Generation and far higher than all vendors in the U.S. classified by this NAICS category.
 

 


